Run Instructions
----------------

Run the main method of com.digitalreasoning.langprocessing.main.RunLangProcessing
Junit test at test.com.digitalreasoning.langprocessing.main.LangFileReaderTest

Design description
------------------
Instance of model.FileToBeAnalyzed relates to parsed output of one file and
contains a list of sentences. Sentences are modeled by model.Sentence. Sentence
contains list of words.A word is modelted by model.Word.

An instance of LangFileReader needs to be passed a filename and its method
readandParse should be called. 
The method toXML will return an XML representation.

Assumptions
-----------


Limitations
-----------
Will not handle very large files well, because all the contents are read into 
memory as one string.


Other Approaches
----------------